overview: Lucas Entertainment catches the raunchiest, nastiest toe-sucking pigs tearing into each other without abandon, featuring Lucas Entertainment Exclusives: Michael Lucas, Matan Shalev, Dimitri Romanov, and Valentin Petrov, along with scorching-hot Rafael Alencar, Arpad Miklos, Manuel Torres, Andrew James, and hot newcomer Johnny Angel.
title: Feet Extreme!
